name: Voice
text: Don't ask me, I don't know either

name: Bob
text: And I thought you are all-knowing...

name: Voice
text: Well, I'm just a voice, okay?

name: Bob
text: Hi, you seems familiar. Did you went to the supermarket near the townhall a week ago?

name: Dovic
text: I'm afraid you're mistaken but a lot of people said it to me earlier

name: Bob
text: Ah okay, that's all right. Fight?
